#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. HTML: </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:0.3"
msgid "Saṃ­ghā­di­sesa­kaṇḍa"
msgstr "Monks’ Suspension"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:0.4"
msgid "Duṭṭha­dosa­sikkhā­pada"
msgstr "8. The training rule on anger"

#. HTML: </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-vp-pli3.158, pts-vp-en1.271, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.1, ms1V_1556 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalanda­ka­nivāpe."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Rājagaha in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrel sanctuary."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmatā dabbena mallaputtena jātiyā sattavassena arahattaṃ sacchikataṃ hoti."
msgstr "At that time Venerable Dabba the Mallian had realized perfection at the age of seven."

#. VAR: Yaṃ kiñci → yañca kiñci (si, mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.3"
msgid "Yaṃ kiñci sāvakena pattabbaṃ sabbaṃ tena anuppattaṃ hoti."
msgstr "He had realized all there is to be realized by a disciple"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.4"
msgid "Natthi cassa kiñci uttari karaṇīyaṃ, katassa vā paticayo."
msgstr "and had nothing further to do."

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.272
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi—"
msgstr "While he was in seclusion he reflected on this, and he thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.6"
msgid "“mayā kho jātiyā sattavassena arahattaṃ sacchikataṃ."
msgstr "“How may I be of service to the Order?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.7"
msgid "Yaṃ kiñci sāvakena pattabbaṃ sabbaṃ mayā anuppattaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.8"
msgid "Natthi ca me kiñci uttari karaṇīyaṃ, katassa vā paticayo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.9"
msgid "Kiṃ nu kho ahaṃ saṃghassa veyyāvaccaṃ kareyyan”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2, ms1V_1557 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.10"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa etadahosi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.1.11"
msgid "“yannūnāhaṃ saṃghassa senāsanañca paññapeyyaṃ bhattāni ca uddiseyyan”ti."
msgstr "Perhaps I could assign dwellings for the Order and designate the meals?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.2
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā dabbo mallaputto sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "In the evening Dabba came out of seclusion and approached the Master."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.2"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "He bowed down to him, sat down to one side,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā dabbo mallaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.4"
msgid "“idha mayhaṃ, bhante, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi mayā kho jātiyā sattavassena arahattaṃ sacchikataṃ, yaṃ kiñci sāvakena pattabbaṃ, sabbaṃ mayā anupattaṃ, natthi ca me kiñci uttari karaṇīyaṃ, katassa vā paticayo, kiṃ nu kho ahaṃ saṃghassa veyyāvaccaṃ kareyyanti."
msgstr "“Venerable Sir, while I was in seclusion I reflected that I’ve attained all that can be attained by a disciple, and I was wondering how I might be of service to the Order."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.5"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, etadahosi—"
msgstr "I thought"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.6"
msgid "‘yannūnāhaṃ saṃghassa senāsanañca paññapeyyaṃ bhattāni ca uddiseyyan’ti."
msgstr "I could assign dwellings for the Order and designate the meals.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.7"
msgid "Icchāmahaṃ, bhante, saṃghassa senāsanañca paññapetuṃ bhattāni ca uddisitun”ti."
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.8"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, dabba."
msgstr "“Well then, Dabba,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.9"
msgid "Tena hi tvaṃ, dabba, saṃghassa senāsanañca paññapehi bhattāni ca uddisā”ti."
msgstr "please do so.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.2.10"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā dabbo mallaputto bhagavato paccassosi."
msgstr "“Ok.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.3, ms1V_1558 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etasmiṃ nidāne etasmiṃ pakaraṇe dhammiṃ kathaṃ katvā bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Soon afterwards the Master gave a teaching and addressed the monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.2"
msgid "“tena hi, bhikkhave, saṃgho dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ senāsa­na­paññā­pakañca bhat­tuddesa­kañca sammannatu."
msgstr "“Monks, the Order should appoint Dabba the Mallian as the assigner of dwellings and the designator of meals."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.3"
msgid "Evañca pana, bhikkhave, sammannitabbo."
msgstr "And he shoud be appointed in this way."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ dabbo mallaputto yācitabbo."
msgstr "First Dabba should be asked."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.5"
msgid "Yācitvā byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṃgho ñāpetabbo—"
msgstr "A competent and capable monk should then inform the Order:"

#. HTML: </p><div class="kamma"><p>
#. REF: sc4, pts-vp-pli3.159, ms1V_1559 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.6"
msgid "‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "‘Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.7"
msgid "Yadi saṃghassa pattakallaṃ saṃgho āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ senāsa­na­paññā­pakañca bhat­tuddesa­kañca sammanneyya."
msgstr "If it seems appropriate to the Order, it should appoint Venerable Dabba the Mallian as assigner of dwellings and designator of meals."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.8"
msgid "Esā ñatti."
msgstr "This is the motion."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5, ms1V_1560 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.9"
msgid "Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.10"
msgid "Saṃgho āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ senāsa­na­paññā­pakañca bhat­tuddesa­kañca sammannati."
msgstr "The Order appoints Venerable Dabba the Mallian as assigner of dwellings and designator of meals."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.11"
msgid "Yassāyasmato khamati āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa senāsa­na­paññā­pakassa ca bhat­tuddesa­kassa ca sammuti, so tuṇhassa;"
msgstr "Any monk who approves of appointing Venerable Dabba the Mallian as assigner of dwellings and designator of meals should remain silent."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.12"
msgid "yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya."
msgstr "Any monk who does not approve should speak up."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6, ms1V_1561, pts-vp-en1.273
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.13"
msgid "Sammato saṃghena āyasmā dabbo mallaputto senāsa­na­paññā­pako ca bhattuddesako ca."
msgstr "The Order has appointed Venerable Dabba the Mallian as assigner of dwellings and designator of meals."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.14"
msgid "Khamati saṃghassa, tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "The Order approves and is therefore silent."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.3.15"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.’”"

#. HTML: </p></div><p>
#. REF: sc7, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.4, ms1V_1562 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.1"
msgid "Sammato ca panāyasmā dabbo mallaputto sabhāgānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti."
msgstr "Dabba assigned dwellings to the monks according to their character."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.2"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū suttantikā tesaṃ ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "He assigned dwellings in the same place to those monks who were discourse experts, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.3"
msgid "“te aññamaññaṃ suttantaṃ saṅgāyissantī”ti."
msgstr "“They’ll recite the discourses together.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.4"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū vinayadharā tesaṃ ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "And he did likewise for the experts on monastic law, thinking,"

#. VAR: vinicchi­nis­santī”ti → vinicchis­santīti (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.5"
msgid "“te aññamaññaṃ vinayaṃ vinicchi­nis­santī”ti."
msgstr "“They’ll deliberate on the monastic law;”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.6"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū dhammakathikā tesaṃ ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "for the expounders of the Teaching, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.7"
msgid "“te aññamaññaṃ dhammaṃ sākacchissantī”ti."
msgstr "“They’ll discuss the Teaching;”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.8"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū jhāyino tesaṃ ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "for the meditators, thinking,"

#. VAR: na byābādhissantī”ti → na byā­bāhis­santīti (mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.9"
msgid "“te aññamaññaṃ na byābādhissantī”ti."
msgstr "“They won’t disturb each other;”"

#. VAR: kāya­daḷhi­bahulā → kāya­daḍḍhi­bahulā (bj) | kāya­daḷhī­bahulā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.10"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū tiracchā­na­ka­thikā kāya­daḷhi­bahulā viharanti tesampi ekajjhaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "and for the gossips and the body-builders, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.11"
msgid "“imāyapime āyasmanto ratiyā acchissantī”ti."
msgstr "“In this way even these venerables will be happy.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-en1.274
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.12"
msgid "Yepi te bhikkhū vikāle āgacchanti tesampi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā teneva ālokena senāsanaṃ paññapeti."
msgstr "When monks arrived at night, he entered the fire element and assigned dwellings with the help of that light."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.13"
msgid "Apisu bhikkhū sañcicca vikāle āgacchanti—"
msgstr "Monks even arrived late on purpose,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.14"
msgid "“mayaṃ āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa iddhi­pā­ṭihā­ri­yaṃ passissāmā”ti."
msgstr "hoping to see the marvel of Dabba’s supernormal powers."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8, pts-vp-pli3.160, ms1V_1563 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.15"
msgid "Te āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evaṃ vadanti—"
msgstr "They would approach Dabba and say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.16"
msgid "“amhākaṃ, āvuso dabba, senāsanaṃ paññapehī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Dabba, assign us a dwelling.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.17"
msgid "Te āyasmā dabbo mallaputto evaṃ vadeti—"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.18
msgid "“katthāyasmantā icchanti, kattha paññapemī”ti?"
msgstr "“Where would you like to stay?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-en1.275
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.19"
msgid "Te sañcicca dūre apadisanti—"
msgstr "They would intentionally suggest somewhere far away,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.20"
msgid "“amhākaṃ, āvuso dabba, gijjhakūṭe pabbate senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "“Please give us a dwelling on Mount Vulture Peak/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.21"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, corapapāte senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "at Robbers’ Cliff/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.22"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, isigilipasse kāḷasilāyaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "on Black Rock on the slope of Mount Isigili/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.23"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, vebhārapasse satta­paṇṇi­guhā­yaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "in the Sattapaṇṇi Cave on the slope of Mount Vebhāra/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.24"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, sītavane sappa­soṇḍi­ka­pabbhāre senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "in Cool Grove on the hill at the Snake’s Pool/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.25"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, gotama­ka­kanda­rā­yaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "at Gomaṭa Gorge/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.26"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, tin­du­ka­kanda­rā­yaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "at Tinduka Gorge/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.27"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, tapoda­kanda­rā­yaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "at Tapoda Gorge/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.28"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, tapodārāme senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "in Tapoda Park/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.29"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, jīvakambavane senāsanaṃ paññapehi."
msgstr "in Jīvaka’s Mango Grove/"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.30"
msgid "Amhākaṃ, āvuso, madda­kucchis­miṃ migadāye senāsanaṃ paññapehī”ti."
msgstr "in the deer park at Maddakucchi.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9, ms1V_1564 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.31"
msgid "Tesaṃ āyasmā dabbo mallaputto tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā aṅguliyā jalamānāya purato purato gacchati."
msgstr "Dabba then entered the fire element, and with his finger glowing, he walked in front of those monks."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.32"
msgid "Tepi teneva ālokena āyasmato dabbassa mallaputtassa piṭṭhito piṭṭhito gacchanti."
msgstr "They followed closely behind him with the help of that light."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.33"
msgid "Tesaṃ āyasmā dabbo mallaputto evaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapeti—"
msgstr "And he would assign them dwellings:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.34"
msgid "“ayaṃ mañco, idaṃ pīṭhaṃ, ayaṃ bhisi, idaṃ bibbohanaṃ, idaṃ vaccaṭṭhānaṃ, idaṃ passāvaṭṭhānaṃ, idaṃ pānīyaṃ, idaṃ paribhojanīyaṃ, ayaṃ kattaradaṇḍo,"
msgstr "“This is the bed, this the bench, this the mattress, this the pillow, this the restroom, this the urinal, this the drinking water, this the water for washing, this the walking stick;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.35"
msgid "idaṃ saṃghassa katika­saṇ­ṭhānaṃ, imaṃ kālaṃ pavisitabbaṃ, imaṃ kālaṃ nikkhamitabban”ti."
msgstr "these are the Order’s agreements, this the time to enter, this the time to depart.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.4.36"
msgid "Tesaṃ āyasmā dabbo mallaputto evaṃ senāsanaṃ paññapetvā punadeva veḷuvanaṃ paccāgacchati."
msgstr "Dabba then returned to the Bamboo Grove."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: metti­ya­bhūma­jakā → metti­ya­bhumma­jakā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. REF: sc10, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.5, ms1V_1565
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū navakā ceva honti appapuññā ca."
msgstr "At that time the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka had recently been given the full ordination."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.2"
msgid "Yāni saṃghassa lāmakāni senāsanāni tāni tesaṃ pāpuṇanti lāmakāni ca bhattāni."
msgstr "They had little merit, and they obtained inferior dwellings and meals."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena rājagahe manussā icchanti therānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ abhi­saṅ­khā­ri­kaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ dātuṃ sappimpi telampi uttari­bhaṅgampi."
msgstr "The people of Rājagaha were keen to give specially prepared almsfood to the senior monks—ghee, oil, and special foods—"

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.276
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.4"
msgid "Metti­ya­bhūma­ja­kānaṃ pana bhikkhūnaṃ pākatikaṃ denti yathārandhaṃ kaṇājakaṃ bilaṅgadutiyaṃ."
msgstr "but to the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka they gave ordinary food of porridge and broken rice."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.5"
msgid "Te pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍa­pāta­paṭik­kantā there bhikkhū pucchanti—"
msgstr "After the meal, when they had returned from almsround, they asked the senior monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.6"
msgid "“tumhākaṃ, āvuso, bhattagge kiṃ ahosi?"
msgstr "“What did you get at the dining hall?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.7"
msgid "Tumhākaṃ, āvuso, bhattagge kiṃ ahosī”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.8"
msgid "Ekacce therā evaṃ vadanti—"
msgstr "Some said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.9"
msgid "“amhākaṃ, āvuso, sappi ahosi telaṃ ahosi uttaribhaṅgaṃ ahosī”ti."
msgstr "“We got ghee, oil, and special foods.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.10"
msgid "Metti­ya­bhūma­jakā pana bhikkhū evaṃ vadanti—"
msgstr "But the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.5.11"
msgid "“amhākaṃ, āvuso, na kiñci ahosi, pākatikaṃ yathārandhaṃ kaṇājakaṃ bilaṅgadutiyan”ti."
msgstr "“We didn’t get anything except ordinary food of porridge and broken rice.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11, pts-vp-pli3.161, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.6, ms1V_1566 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati saṃghassa catukkabhattaṃ deti niccabhattaṃ."
msgstr "At that time there was a lay person who gave a regular meal of fine food to four monks."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.2"
msgid "So bhattagge saputtadāro upatiṭṭhitvā parivisati."
msgstr "He made his offering in the dining hall together with his wives and children."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.3"
msgid "Aññe odanena pucchanti, aññe sūpena pucchanti, aññe telena pucchanti, aññe uttaribhaṅgena pucchanti."
msgstr "Some of them offered rice, others curries, others oil, and others special foods."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.4"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena kal­yāṇa­bhatti­kassa gahapatino bhattaṃ svātanāya metti­ya­bhūma­ja­kānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ uddiṭṭhaṃ hoti."
msgstr "On one occasion the meal to be given by this lay person on the following day had been designated to the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.5"
msgid "Atha kho kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati ārāmaṃ agamāsi kenacideva karaṇīyena."
msgstr "Just then that lay person went to the monastery on some business."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.6"
msgid "So yenāyasmā dabbo mallaputto tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He approached Dabba,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.7"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "bowed down to him, and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.8"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho kal­yāṇa­bhatti­kaṃ gahapatiṃ āyasmā dabbo mallaputto dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi."
msgstr "Dabba then instructed, inspired, and gladdened him with a teaching."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.9"
msgid "Atha kho kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati āyasmatā dabbena mallaputtena dhammiyā kathāya sandassito samādapito samuttejito sampahaṃsito āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "After the talk, he asked Dabba,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.10"
msgid "“kassa, bhante, amhākaṃ ghare svātanāya bhattaṃ uddiṭṭhan”ti?"
msgstr "“Venerable, who has been designated to receive tomorrow’s meal in our house?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.11"
msgid "“Metti­ya­bhūma­ja­kānaṃ kho, gahapati, bhikkhūnaṃ tumhākaṃ ghare svātanāya bhattaṃ uddiṭṭhan”ti."
msgstr "“Mettiya and Bhūmajaka.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-en1.277
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.12"
msgid "Atha kho kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati anattamano ahosi—"
msgstr "He was disappointed, and thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.13"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma pāpabhikkhū amhākaṃ ghare bhuñjissantī”ti."
msgstr "“Why should bad monks eat in our house?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.14"
msgid "Gharaṃ gantvā dāsiṃ āṇāpesi—"
msgstr "After returning to his house, he told a female slave,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.15"
msgid "“ye, je, sve bhattikā āgacchanti te koṭṭhake āsanaṃ paññapetvā kaṇājakena bilaṅ­ga­duti­yena parivisā”ti."
msgstr "“For those who are coming for tomorrow’s meal, prepare seats at the gateway and serve them broken rice and porridge.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.6.16"
msgid "“Evaṃ, ayyā”ti kho sā dāsī kal­yāṇa­bhatti­kassa gahapatino paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.7, ms1V_1567 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.1"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū—"
msgstr "The monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka said to one another,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.2"
msgid "“hiyyo kho, āvuso, amhākaṃ kal­yāṇa­bhatti­kassa gahapatino bhattaṃ uddiṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr "“Yesterday we were designated a meal from that lay person who offers fine food."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.3"
msgid "sve amhe kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati saputtadāro upatiṭṭhitvā parivisissati;"
msgstr "Tomorrow he’ll serve us together with his wives and children."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.4"
msgid "aññe odanena pucchissanti, aññe sūpena pucchissanti, aññe telena pucchissanti, aññe uttaribhaṅgena pucchissantī”ti."
msgstr "Some of them will offer us rice, others curry, others oil, and others special foods.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.5"
msgid "Te teneva somanassena na cittarūpaṃ rattiyā supiṃsu."
msgstr "And because they were excited, they did not sleep properly that night."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13, pts-vp-pli3.162, ms1V_1568 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.6"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū pubbaṇ­ha­samayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaraṃ ādāya yena kal­yāṇa­bhatti­kassa gahapatino nivesanaṃ tenu­pasaṅka­miṃsu."
msgstr "The following morning they robed up, took their bowls and robes, and went to the house of that lay person."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.7"
msgid "Addasā kho sā dāsī metti­ya­bhūma­jake bhikkhū dūratova āgacchante."
msgstr "When the female slave saw them coming,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.8"
msgid "Disvāna koṭṭhake āsanaṃ paññapetvā metti­ya­bhūma­jake bhikkhū etadavoca—"
msgstr "she prepared seats at the gateway and said to them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.9"
msgid "“nisīdatha, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Please sit, Venerables.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-en1.278
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.10"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­ja­kānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ etadahosi—"
msgstr "They thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.11"
msgid "“nissaṃsayaṃ kho na tāva bhattaṃ siddhaṃ bhavissati."
msgstr "“The meal can’t be ready,"

#. VAR: mayaṃ koṭṭhake nisīdeyyāmā”ti → nisī­dāpi­yey­yāmāti (bj) | nisīdāpiyāmāti (s1-3) | nisī­dāpeyyā­māti (pts1)
#. VAR: Yathā → yāva (bj)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.12"
msgid "Yathā mayaṃ koṭṭhake nisīdeyyāmā”ti."
msgstr "since we’re given seats at the gateway.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.13"
msgid "Atha kho sā dāsī kaṇājakena bilaṅ­ga­duti­yena upagacchi—"
msgstr "She then brought them broken rice and porridge, and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.14"
msgid "“bhuñjatha, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Eat, Venerables.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.15"
msgid "“Mayaṃ kho, bhagini, niccabhattikā”ti."
msgstr "“But, Sister, we’ve come for the regular meal.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: nicca­bhatti­kāti → nicca­bhatti­kat­tha (bj) | nicca­bhatti­kāt­tha (c1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.16"
msgid "“Jānāmi, ayyā, nicca­bhatti­kāti."
msgstr "“I know."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.17"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ hiyyova gahapatinā āṇattā—"
msgstr "But yesterday I was told by our master"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.18"
msgid "‘ye, je, sve bhattikā āgacchanti te koṭṭhake āsanaṃ paññapetvā kaṇājakena bilaṅ­ga­duti­yena parivisā’ti."
msgstr "to serve you like this."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.19"
msgid "Bhuñjatha, bhante”ti."
msgstr "Please eat.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.20"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū—"
msgstr "They said to each other,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.21"
msgid "“hiyyo kho, āvuso, kal­yāṇa­bhattiko gahapati ārāmaṃ agamāsi dabbassa mallaputtassa santike."
msgstr "“Yesterday this lay person came to the monastery and spoke with Dabba."

#. VAR: antare → santike (bj, s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.22"
msgid "Nissaṃsayaṃ kho mayaṃ dabbena mallaputtena gahapatino antare paribhinnā”ti."
msgstr "Dabba must be responsible for this split between us and this lay person.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.23"
msgid "Te teneva domanassena na cittarūpaṃ bhuñjiṃsu."
msgstr "And because they were dejected, they did not eat as much as they had intended."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.7.24"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍa­pāta­paṭik­kantā ārāmaṃ gantvā pattacīvaraṃ paṭisāmetvā ­bahārā­ma­koṭṭhake saṅghā­ṭi­pal­latthi­kāya nisīdiṃsu tuṇhībhūtā maṅkubhūtā pattakkhandhā adhomukhā pajjhāyantā appaṭibhānā."
msgstr "After the meal they returned to the monastery, put their bowls and robes away, and squatted on their heels outside the monastery gateway, supported by their outer robe. They were silent and humiliated, their shoulders drooping and their heads down, glum and speechless."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.8, pts-vp-en1.279, ms1V_1569 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.1"
msgid "Atha kho mettiyā bhikkhunī yena metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Just then the nun Mettiyā approached them"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.2"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā metti­ya­bhūma­jake bhikkhū etadavoca—"
msgstr "and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.3"
msgid "“vandāmi, ayyā”ti."
msgstr "“I pay respect to you, Venerables.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū nālapiṃsu."
msgstr "But they did not respond."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.5"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho … pe …"
msgstr "A second time"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.6"
msgid "tatiyampi kho mettiyā bhikkhunī metti­ya­bhūma­jake bhikkhū etadavoca—"
msgstr "and a third time she said"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.7"
msgid "“vandāmi, ayyā”ti."
msgstr "the same thing,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.8"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū nālapiṃsu."
msgstr "but they still did not respond."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.9"
msgid "“Kyāhaṃ ayyānaṃ aparajjhāmi?"
msgstr "“Have I done something wrong?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.10"
msgid "Kissa maṃ ayyā nālapantī”ti?"
msgstr "Why don’t you respond?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.11"
msgid "“Tathā hi pana tvaṃ, bhagini, amhe dabbena mallaputtena viheṭhīyamāne ajjhupekkhasī”ti?"
msgstr "“It’s because we’ve been badly treated by Dabba the Mallian, and you’re not taking an interest.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.12"
msgid "“Kyāhaṃ, ayyā, karomī”ti?"
msgstr "“What can I do?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.13"
msgid "“Sace kho tvaṃ, bhagini, iccheyyāsi ajjeva bhagavā dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ nāsāpeyyā”ti."
msgstr "“If you like, you could make the Master eject Dabba.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.14"
msgid "“Kyāhaṃ, ayyā, karomi,"
msgstr "“What should I do?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.15"
msgid "kiṃ mayā sakkā kātun”ti?"
msgstr "How am I able to do that?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.16"
msgid "“Ehi tvaṃ, bhagini, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkama;"
msgstr "“Go to the Master"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.17"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ evaṃ vadehi—"
msgstr "and say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.18"
msgid "‘idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ."
msgstr "‘Venerable Sir, this is not proper or appropriate."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.19"
msgid "Yāyaṃ, bhante, disā abhayā anītikā anupaddavā sāyaṃ disā sabhayā saītikā saupaddavā."
msgstr "There’s fear, distress, and oppression in this district, where none of these should exist."

#. VAR: savātaṃ → pavātaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.20"
msgid "Yato nivātaṃ tato savātaṃ."
msgstr "From where one would expect security, there’s insecurity."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.21"
msgid "Udakaṃ maññe ādittaṃ."
msgstr "It’s as if water is burning."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.22"
msgid "Ayyenamhi dabbena mallaputtena dūsitā’”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Dabba the Mallian has raped me.’”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.23"
msgid "“Evaṃ, ayyā”ti kho mettiyā bhikkhunī metti­ya­bhūma­ja­kānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "“Very well, sirs,” and she approached the Master,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.24"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr "bowed down to him, and stood to one side."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.25"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā mettiyā bhikkhunī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "She then repeated what she had been told to say."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.26"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.27"
msgid "Yāyaṃ, bhante, disā abhayā anītikā anupaddavā sāyaṃ disā sabhayā saītikā saupaddavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.28"
msgid "Yato nivātaṃ tato savātaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.29"
msgid "Udakaṃ maññe ādittaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.8.30"
msgid "Ayyenamhi dabbena mallaputtena dūsitā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15, pts-vp-pli3.163, pts-cs-bu-ss8.1.9, pts-vp-en1.280, ms1V_1570 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etasmiṃ nidāne etasmiṃ pakaraṇe bhikkhusaṃghaṃ sannipātāpetvā āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ paṭipucchi—"
msgstr "Soon afterwards the Master had the Order of monks assembled and asked Dabba,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.2"
msgid "“sarasi tvaṃ, dabba, evarūpaṃ kattā yathāyaṃ bhikkhunī āhā”ti?"
msgstr "“Dabba, do you remember doing as the nun Mettiyā says?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.3"
msgid "“Yathā maṃ, bhante, bhagavā jānātī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Sir, the Master knows about me.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.4"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "A second and"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.5"
msgid "tatiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "a third time the Master asked"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.6"
msgid "“sarasi tvaṃ, dabba, evarūpaṃ kattā yathāyaṃ bhikkhunī āhā”ti?"
msgstr "the same question"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.7"
msgid "“Yathā maṃ, bhante, bhagavā jānātī”ti."
msgstr "and got the same response."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.8"
msgid "“Na kho, dabba, dabbā evaṃ nibbeṭhenti."
msgstr "He then said, “Dabba, the Dabbas don’t give such evasive answers."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.9"
msgid "Sace tayā kataṃ katanti vadehi,"
msgstr "If it was done by you, say so;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.10"
msgid "sace tayā akataṃ akatanti vadehī”ti."
msgstr "if it wasn’t done by you, then say that.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.11"
msgid "“Yato ahaṃ, bhante, jāto nābhijānāmi supinantenapi methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevitā, pageva jāgaro”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Sir, since I was born I don’t recall having sexual intercourse even in a dream, much less when I was awake.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.12"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "The Master addressed the monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.13"
msgid "“tena hi, bhikkhave, mettiyaṃ bhikkhuniṃ nāsetha."
msgstr "“Well then, monks, eject the nun Mettiyā,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.14"
msgid "Ime ca bhikkhū anuyuñjathā”ti."
msgstr "and call these monks to account.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.15"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā bhagavā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ pāvisi."
msgstr "The Master then rose from his seat and entered his dwelling."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16, ms1V_1571 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.16"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū mettiyaṃ bhikkhuniṃ nāsesuṃ."
msgstr "When the monks had ejected the nun Mettiyā,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.17"
msgid "Atha kho metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū te bhikkhū etadavocuṃ—"
msgstr "the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka said to them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.18"
msgid "“māvuso, mettiyaṃ bhikkhuniṃ nāsetha."
msgstr "“Don’t eject the nun Mettiyā;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.19"
msgid "Na sā kiñci aparajjhati."
msgstr "she’s done nothing wrong."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.20"
msgid "Amhehi sā ussāhitā kupitehi anattamanehi cāvanā­dhip­pā­yehī”ti."
msgstr "She was urged on by us, because we were angry, displeased, and aiming to make Dabba leave the monastic life.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.21"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana tumhe, āvuso, āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ amūlakena pārājikena dhammena anuddhaṃsethā”ti?"
msgstr "“But did you groundlessly accuse Venerable Dabba of an offense entailing expulsion?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.22"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti."
msgstr "“Yes.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.23"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.281
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.24"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.25"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma metti­ya­bhūma­jakā bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ amūlakena pārājikena dhammena anuddhaṃ­ses­santī”ti."
msgstr "“How can the monks Mettiya and Bhūmajaka groundlessly accuse Venerable Dabba of an offense entailing expulsion?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17, ms1V_1572 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.26"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū metti­ya­bhūma­jake bhikkhū aneka­pariyā­yena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They rebuked those monks in many ways and then told the Master. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.27"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ amūlakena pārājikena dhammena anuddhaṃsethā”ti?"
msgstr "He said, “Is it true, monks, that you groundlessly accused Dabba the Mallian of an offense entailing expulsion?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.28"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.29"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.30"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma tumhe, moghapurisā, dabbaṃ mallaputtaṃ amūlakena pārājikena dhammena anuddhaṃ­ses­sa­tha."
msgstr "Foolish men, how can you groundlessly accuse Dabba of an offense entailing expulsion?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.31"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.32"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.32a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc18, ms1V_1573
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.33"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu bhikkhuṃ duṭṭho doso appatīto amūlakena pārājikena dhammena anuddhaṃseyya—"
msgstr "‘If a monk who is angry and displeased groundlessly accuses another monk of an offense entailing expulsion,"

#. VAR: appeva nāma → appevanāma (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss8:1.9.34"
msgid "‘appeva nāma naṃ imamhā brahmacariyā cāveyyan’ti, tato aparena samayena sama­nug­gāhīya­māno vā asama­nug­gāhīya­māno vā amūlakañceva taṃ adhikaraṇaṃ hoti bhikkhu ca dosaṃ patiṭṭhāti, saṃghādiseso”ti."
msgstr "aiming to make him leave the monastic life, and then after some time, whether he is questioned or not, it is clear that the legal issue is groundless, and he admits to his ill-will, he commits an offense entailing suspension.’”"

